msgid "Using the Project Manager"
msgstr "專案管理員"

msgid ""
"When you launch Godot, the first window you see is the Project Manager. It "
"lets you create, remove, import, or play game projects."
msgstr ""
"啟動 Godot 後看到的第一個視窗就是專案管理員了。由於目前還沒有專案，所以會出現"
"一個彈窗詢問是否開啟素材庫，這裡先點 [取消]，我們晚點再回來看。"

msgid ""
"In the window's top-right corner, a drop-down menu allows you to change the "
"editor's language."
msgstr "你可以通過視窗的右上角的下拉式功能表來更改編輯器的語言。"

msgid "Creating and importing projects"
msgstr "建立新專案"

msgid "To create a new project:"
msgstr "建立新專案"

#, fuzzy
msgid "Click the **New** button on the top-left of the window."
msgstr "按一下視窗右側的 ``新建專案`` 按鈕。"

msgid ""
"Give the project a name, choose an empty folder on your computer to save the "
"files, and select a rendering backend."
msgstr "為專案命名，在電腦上選擇一個空資料夾來保存檔，然後選擇算繪後端。"

#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Click the **Create & Edit** button to create the project folder and open it "
"in the editor."
msgstr "按一下“匯入並編輯”按鈕，這樣就會建立專案檔案夾並將其在編輯器中打開。"

msgid "Using the file browser"
msgstr "提供檔案"

#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Click the **Browse** button to open Godot's file browser and pick a location "
"or type the folder's path in the Project Path field."
msgstr ""
"按一下“瀏覽”按鈕打開 Godot 的檔瀏覽器，然後選中某個位置，或者在 \\\\\\\\*專案"
"路徑* \\\\\\\\欄位中輸入資料夾的路徑。"

#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"When you see the green tick on the right, it means the engine detects an "
"empty folder. You can also click the **Create Folder** button to create an "
"empty folder based on your project's name."
msgstr ""
"當你看到右側的綠色勾號時，表示引擎偵測到一個空資料夾。 你還可以按一下 ``建立"
"資料夾`` 按鈕以根據你的專案名稱建立一個空資料夾。"

msgid "Opening and importing projects"
msgstr "建立新專案"

msgid ""
"The next time you open the Project Manager, you'll see your new project in "
"the list. Double click on it to open it in the editor."
msgstr ""
"下次打開專案管理器時，你將在列表中看到你的新專案。 按兩下它以在編輯器中將它打"
"開。"

#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You can similarly import existing projects using the **Import** button. "
"Locate the folder that contains the project or the **project.godot** file to "
"import and edit it."
msgstr ""
"同樣地你可以使用*匯入*按鈕匯入現有專案。 找到包含專案或 ``project.godot`` 檔"
"的資料夾以匯入並編輯它。"

msgid "When the folder path is correct, you'll see a green checkmark."
msgstr "當資料夾路徑正確時，你會看到一個綠色的對勾。"

msgid "Downloading demos and templates"
msgstr "建置匯出樣板"

msgid ""
"From the **Asset Library Projects** tab you can download open source project "
"templates and demos from the :ref:`Asset Library <doc_what_is_assetlib>` to "
"help you get started faster."
msgstr ""
"在**素材庫專案**分頁中，你可以從:ref:`素材庫 <doc_what_is_assetlib>`下載開源"
"專案範本和演示程式，以便更快地開始。"

msgid "To download a demo or template:"
msgstr "以及包含 Mono 的匯出樣板："

msgid "Click on its title."
msgstr "點擊它的標題。"

msgid "On the page that opens, click the download button."
msgstr "要打開匯出選單，請點擊 **[匯出]** 按鈕："

msgid ""
"Once it finished downloading, click install and choose where you want to "
"save the project."
msgstr "一旦下載完成，點擊\\\\\\\\*安裝*並選擇你想要保存專案的位置。"

msgid "Translation status"
msgstr "翻譯狀態"
